<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Clarify said lowered.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Clarify said lowered.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- PaineWebber downgraded Clarify Inc to neutral from buy, market sources said.</p>
<p>-- The analyst was not immediately available for comment.</p>
<p>-- Late Tuesday the company said it expects little, if any revenue growth in the second quarter of 1997 from the first quarter.</p>
<p>-- Its shares sank 9-1/2 to 7-1/4.</p>
</text>
